{"word":"Temperance-Intemperance","slug":"temperance-intemperance","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Temperance-Intemperance</b> - <b>(A) TEMPERANCE</b> (Select Readings)<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=23&verse=1'>Pro 23:1-35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=1'>Isa 5:1-30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=28&verse=1'>Isa 28:1-29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=1'>Dan 1:1-21</a><p/><b>(1) General References to</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=21&verse=17'>Pro 21:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=23&verse=1'>Pro 23:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=23&verse=2'>Pro 23:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=25&verse=16'>Pro 25:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=25'>Act 24:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=25'>1Co 9:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=23'>Gal 5:23</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=2'>Tit 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=6'>2Pe 1:6</a><p/><b>(2) Total Abstinence from Strong Drink</b><p/><b>Enjoined upon the Priests</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=9'>Le 10:9</a><p/><b>Law from the Nazarites</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=3'>Num 6:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=6'>Deu 29:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=13&verse=4'>Jdg 13:4</a><p/><b>The Wise Man's Injunction</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=23&verse=31'>Pr 23:31</a><p/><b>Rule for Kings</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chap